      "body" : "@AndyThomas No, I was actually asking for the exact opposite of <code>assertArrayEquals</code> which would be <code>assertArrayNotEquals</code> (it does not exist). But I just realized, when testing for inequality, the meaning of &quot;assertion failed&quot; is enough, because all the elements are equal, so there is no need for a comparison output. So you actually answered my question with <code>Arrays.equals</code>."
